### Get All restaurants
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants

### Get All restaurants by filters
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants?name=Pahad%20poisid2&location=K%C3%BC%C3%BCni%202,%20Tartu,%20Estonia

### Get restaurant by id
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants/1

### Add a restaurant
POST http://localhost:8080/restaurants
Content-Type: application/json

