### Get Menu by Restaurant ID
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants/:id/menu

### Create a Menu
POST http://localhost:8080/restaurants/:id/menu
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lastUpdated": "2024-03-13T08:00:00"
}

### Delete Menu by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/restaurants/:id/menu/:menuId

### Get All Menu Items by Restaurant ID and Menu ID
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants/:id/menu/:menuId/items

### Get Menu Item by Restaurant ID, Menu ID, and Item ID
GET http://localhost:8080/restaurants/:id/menu/:menuId/items/:itemId

### Create a Menu Item
POST http://localhost:8080/restaurants/:id/menu/:menuId/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Chicken Curry",
  "description": "Delicious chicken curry with rice",
  "price": 10.99,
  "category": "Main Course",
  "availability": true,
  "dietaryInfo": "Contains gluten"
}

### Update Menu Item
PUT http://localhost:8080/restaurants/:id/menu/:menuId/items/:itemId
